Verdict: An exceptionally well-researched architecture tailored brilliantly to specific hardware quirks. It loses 1.5 points exclusively for pseudo-code YAML snippets that would break execution for beginners, and a critical Unix permission trap in the mcpo volume mapping. With the exact syntax fixes applied from this audit, it becomes a 10/10 production-grade deployment guide.
